              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>Both partners are willing to attend and engage</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>There's still emotional investment in the relationship</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>Both are open to change and self-reflection</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>You seek help early rather than waiting years</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <CheckCircle class="h-5 w-5 text-green-500 mr-2 mt-0.5" />
                  <span>There's no active abuse or untreated addiction</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

